        "text": "MiroShark PR #30: Full Web Push implementation shipped and merged. Users toggle a 🔔 during simulation runs and get a browser notification when it finishes — even with the tab backgrounded. VAPID key generation, subscription persistence, pywebpush dispatch, service worker, and cleanup on log deletion. Zero external services. Aaron hardened it with fcntl file locking and VAPID key security notes before merge."
