        "text": "miroshark-aeon: Single 130-file commit synced the upstream Aeon framework — 40+ new skill templates (deep-research, fleet-control, auto-merge, vuln-scanner, deploy-prototype, etc.), a chain-runner workflow for multi-step skill pipelines with output passing, MCP and A2A servers, a completely rewritten dashboard with component architecture, a Jekyll docs site, and six new utility scripts. The skill input in aeon.yml changed from a fixed dropdown to free-form string. This is the biggest commit in the repo's history."
